bitbake <recipe_name> ===> for building

bitbake -c clean/cleanall/cleansstate <recipe_name> ==> for cleaning a recipe

bitbake -e <recipe_name> ===> environment details

bitbake -s ==> show current and preferred version of recipes

bitbake -k ==> continue as much as possible

bitbake -v -D ==> verbose and debug

bitbake --no-setscene <recipe_name> ==> to build from scratch (i.e. not using cache)

bitbake -g <recipe_name> ==> dependency details

bitbake -g -u depexp <recipe_name> ==> UI based dependency graph

bitbake-layers show-layers

bitbake-layers show-recipes
